<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Mak Soluções Sustentáveis</title>
<style>
html {
    scroll-behavior: smooth;
}

body {
    font-family: "Inter", Arial, sans-serif;
    margin: 0;
    background-color: #f8fff8;
    color: #111;
    padding-top: 90px;
}

/* Cabeçalho fixo */
header {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    z-index: 1000;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 20px 80px;
    background: rgba(232, 248, 232, 0.95);
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
}

.logo {
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 22px;
    color: #008037;
}

nav a {
    text-decoration: none;
    color: #222;
    margin: 0 15px;
    font-weight: 500;
}

nav a:hover {
    color: #00a74f;
}

.btn-contato {
    background: white;
    border: 2px solid #00a74f;
    color: #00a74f;
    padding: 8px 14px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    cursor: pointer;
}

/* Seções principais */
section {
    padding: 100px 80px;
}

.hero {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-around;
    align-items: center;
    background-color: #eafaea;
}
.hero h1 { color: #00994d; font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 10px; }
.hero p { max-width: 400px; color: #333; margin-bottom: 25px; }
.buttons { display: flex; gap: 10px; }
.btn-green {
    background: #00a74f; color: white; border: none;
    padding: 10px 18px; border-radius: 8px; cursor: pointer;
}
.btn-outline {
    background: white; border: 2px solid #00a74f; color: #00a74f;
    padding: 10px 18px; border-radius: 8px; cursor: pointer;
}

/* Serviços */
#servicos {
    background: #fff;
}
.servico-card {
    background: #eafaea;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 20px;
    margin: 20px 0;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}

/* Blog */
#blog {
    background: #f0fff0;
}
.post {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 20px;
    margin: 25px 0;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}
.post img {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
}

/* Sobre */
#sobre {
    background-color: #eafaea;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 40px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
}
.sobre-texto { flex: 1; }
.sobre-imagem img { width: 100%; border-radius: 10px; }

/* Contato e orçamento */
#contato {
    background: #fff;
}
.formulario {
    background: white;
    padding: 40px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 500px;
    margin: auto;
}
.formulario label { font-weight: 600; color: #333; display:block; margin-bottom:6px;}
.formulario input, .formulario select, .formulario textarea {
    width: 100%; padding: 10px; border:1.5px solid #ccc;
    border-radius:8px; margin-bottom:20px;
}
.formulario button {
    background:#00a74f; color:white; border:none; padding:12px 20px;
    border-radius:8px; cursor:pointer;
}
footer {
    text-align:center;
    padding:30px;
    background-color:#e8f8e8;
    color:#333;
    font-size:14px;
}
</style>

<!-- SOBRE -->
<section id="sobre">
    <div class="sobre-texto">
        <h2>Sobre a <span style="color:#00994d;">MAK</span></h2>
        <p>Somos uma empresa especializada em soluções sustentáveis e energia renovável, comprometida em transformar o cenário energético brasileiro.</p>
        <p>Com mais de 10 anos de experiência no mercado, já realizamos centenas de projetos que reduzem a pegada de carbono e impulsionam a energia limpa.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="sobre-imagem">
        <img src="https://source.unsplash.com/600x400/?solar,panel" alt="Equipe MAK">
    </div>
</section>